data.description: Looking for an updated 5/3 pool home in the heart of Ormond Beach.  Roof was replaced 5 years ago.  A new water heater was installed in 2023.  Home features 2 ac units. One unit replaced in 2022.  One unit is 10 years old working great.  New tile floors downstairs & new LVP floors upstairs.  Master bathroom was completely redone & the upstairs hallway bathroom was completely redone.  New paint in all areas of the home.  All outlets have been updated each room has 1 usb outlet.  Kitchen cabinets have been painted, all new handles & hinges.  New butcher block countertops and backsplash.  Located on a corner lot with Large backyard, with plenty of space to add a deck next to the large inground pool.  New privacy fenced installed 2023.  Custom shelves & peg board installed in garage for tools
